---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Accessibility</h1>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Jean-Louis Guénégo is committed to making the site <strong
        >jlg-consulting.com</strong
      > as accessible as possible to all users, regardless of their abilities.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Scope of the RGAA</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      This website is not subject to the obligations of the RGAA
      (General Reference for Improving Accessibility) because:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <li>It is published personally by an individual,</li>
      <li>It is not under a public organization,</li>
      <li>
        It is not operated by a company providing a public service,
      </li>
      <li>
        It does not exceed 250 million euros in annual revenue.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">
      Consequently, the legal obligation to comply with the RGAA does not apply.
      However, particular attention is paid to readability, ease of use, and
      compatibility with assistive technologies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Continuous Improvement</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      If you notice an accessibility issue or have suggestions to improve the
      experience, you can contact me at:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <li>
        Email: <a
          href="mailto:jlg@jlg-consulting.com"
          class="text-primary-700 underline">jlg@jlg-consulting.com</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Recourse</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      If you believe you have not received a satisfactory response, you can
      contact the Defender of Rights:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <li>
        <a
          href="https://formulaire.defenseurdesdroits.fr"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-primary-700 underline">formulaire.defenseurdesdroits.fr</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        By mail (no postage required): Defender of Rights, Free response 71120, 75342 Paris CEDEX 07
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>